commit 214eef76eb86ef66ddbd7a2b0f734b820843bf35
Author: David Henningsson <david.henningsson@canonical.com>
Date:   Tue Jul 22 14:09:35 2014 +0200

    ALSA: hda - Make vendor quirks lowest prio for ALC2xx
    
    Add a new quirk table to make sure that pin quirks have a higher
    priority than quirks that apply to an entire vendor.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Henningsson <david.henningsson@canonical.com>
    Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

